			<h2 class="second-title">
				4. Le système nerveux :
			</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="w3-container">
			<div class="sub-partie">
				<div class="img-wrap">
					<img class="w3-card-4 w3-animate-opacity" src="/imgs/systeme_nerveux.png" style="width: 60%; display: block; margin-left: 20%;">

					<div class="img-description" style="width: 60%; margin-left: 20%;">
